  "wechat_html": "<img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3hAJnwuyZuicicZkgJBUCCaricdibomDBrTzXgUR7FJnf11qGIo8nmKt6RxibXrb5s4RFb9UZ9UOHQy7fqQyI377Licw/0?wx_fmt=gif' style='width:100%;display:block;'><section style='padding:0;'><section style=\"margin:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f6efe4 0%,#fbf8f2 58%,#ffffff 100%);padding:1px;color:#1f2937;\"><section style=\"width:100%;margin:0;\"><section style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.16);box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:relative;background:#d6d3d1;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-00.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;display:block;\"></div><section style=\"padding:16px 12px 10px;\"><div style=\"display:inline-block;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:999px;background:#111827;color:#f9fafb;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;\">History Today</div><h1 style=\"font-size:29px;line-height:1.22;margin:12px 0 10px;color:#111827;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;\">历史上的今天：公历日期的奥秘</h1><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:#475569;margin:0;\">探索公历日期背后的时间流逝与历法常识。</p></section><section style=\"padding:0 10px 12px;\"><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">在漫长的历史长河中，每一天都有着独特的坐标。当我们翻开日历，3月15日这一天在公历平年中占据着第74天的位置，距离岁末还有291天，若遇闰年则为292天。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-01.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">这种精确的时间划分方式，源于人类对天文规律的长期观测。公历作为目前全球通用的历法，其逻辑严密，通过平年与闰年的交替，精准地校准了地球绕太阳公转的周期。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-02.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">回顾历史，许多重要的时刻都曾被定格在特定的日期上。每一天的更迭，不仅是数字的简单跳动，更是人类文明在时间刻度上留下的深刻印记。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-03.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">时间管理是现代生活的重要课题。了解历法不仅是为了记录过去，更是为了更好地规划未来。每一天的到来，都意味着新的机遇与挑战。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-04.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">让我们珍惜每一个平凡的日期，因为正是这些由数字组成的节点，共同构筑了我们宏大的历史叙事。愿你在每一个平凡的日子里，都能发现不凡的意义。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-05.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div></section></section></section></section></section><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3hAJnwuyZuicicZkgJBUCCaricdibomDBrTzk57DCmhVC16o9ILH0Tn1YPEiarfLRRQSVFN2mJdeYibGnBPialPIzvojw/0?wx_fmt=gif' style='width:100%;display:block;'>"
